<task id="starting_euca_broker">
	<title>Start the VMware Broker</title>
	<shortdesc/>
	<taskbody>
		<context>
			<p>If you are using Eucalyptus with VWware support, start the VMware Broker. The VMware Broker is
			located on the CC.</p>
		</context>
		<steps>
			<step>
				<cmd>Log in to the CC server and enter the following:</cmd>
				<info>
					<codeblock conref="../shared/reuse.dita#reuse/euca_start"/>
				</info>
			</step>
			<step>
				<cmd>Repeat for each CC server.</cmd>
			</step>
		</steps>
	</taskbody>
</task>
